hackathon-description-text: IC Hack is back! Running for its seventh consecutive year, we’re inviting over 300 of the UK’s most creative and talented students to London to hack on any project that takes their fancy for 24 hours.
hackathon-rules: All attendees, sponsors, partners, volunteers and staff at our hackathon are required to agree with the code of conduct.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Note: This prize is if this is your team is more than 50% freshers

hackathon-description-header: Imperial College London's annual student run hackathon, powered by Microsoft
hackathon-location-description: Imperial College London - South Kensington Campus
